content.text: Not much, just editing a video.
I like to make short films with my camcorder.
That sounds fun! Have you ever made a movie about a superhero?
I have not made a superhero movie.. but I dressed up as a superhero and told the police officer I was on my way to save the world.
That is hilarious! Did the police officer believe you?
Not really.. he just laughed and told me to get back in my car.
That is too funny. What is your favorite type of music?
They are great! My mom is a music teacher at the elementary school.
That is cool! I like to stay active and go to the gym 3-4 times a week.
That is awesome.. I do not really have time for that, I work as a dental assistant in a ritzy part of town.
Oh, that sounds like a cool job! What do you like about it?
I like the people I work with.. but I am not sure if I enjoy programming.. it might be my only choice.
Well, you seem to be doing well at your job.
Thanks! I am trying my best.
